OL,5, Thousands of PwC staff are to get a 9% 
OL,6, pay rise in response to rising living  
OL,7, costs and a competitive recruitment    
OL,8, market, the accountancy giant has said.
OL,10,FThe company said half of its more than 
OL,11,F20,000 employees in the UK would get an
OL,12,Fincrease of at least 7%, while 70%     
OL,13,Fwould get a rise of 9% or more.        
OL,15,FWith vacancies at a record high, many  
OL,16,Ffirms are offering pay rises to attract
OL,17,Fand retain staff.                      
OL,19,FBut ministers have warned big salary   
OL,20,Frises could further fuel price rises.  
